  public TabletServers getParticipatingTabletServers(@PathParam("tableId") @NotNull @Pattern(
      regexp = ALPHA_NUM_REGEX_TABLE_ID) String tableIdStr) {

  //Google format
  public TabletServers getParticipatingTabletServers(@PathParam("tableId") @NotNull
  @Pattern(regexp = ALPHA_NUM_REGEX_TABLE_ID) String tableIdStr) {
```
5. Javadoc changes to move variable comments to the same line

```
